            "title": "港股開市︱初段再漲 恒指升198點報27325點 鳴鳴很忙登場高開約88%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段持續升勢，恒生指數開市報27325點，升198點或0.73%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報5786點，升31點或0.56%；國企指數以9302點開市，升58點或0.63%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報170.5元，升0.35%；騰訊(00700)開報613元，升0.99%；美團(03690)開報97元，升0.47%；京東(09618)開報115.2元，升1.5%；小米(01810)開報35.56元，暫時無升跌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兩大藍籌國際金融股同樣高開，滙控(00005)開報137.5元，升2.23%；友邦(01299)開報86.6元，升0.17%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240430_FI_source-web_00005-7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240430_FI_source-web_00005-7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">曹操出行(02643)折讓近9%配股，該股今早應聲受壓，開報34.96元，跌1.96%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">鳴鳴很忙(01768)今早掛牌，以445元開市，較招股價236.6元高88.08%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15618105-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%86%8d%e6%bc%b2-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87198%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b127325%e9%bb%9e-%e9%b3%b4%e9%b3%b4%e5%be%88%e5%bf%99%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4",
